body:
I was gifted the gentleman Poro skin by a friend and when i was playing against a twitch on SR.  I decided to by a greater vision trinket to be able to place in a pinch to be able to see him. Early that game my gentleman was working fine but when i decided to place a vision ward with my trinket and after killed the twitch I looked backed at my ward and realized it was a astronaut poro ward(Placed from the greater vision trinket).

1. In Game after getting level 9 so your able to buy the grater stealth trinket and place a ward with the trinket. {{item:3362}} 
2. Also buy a basic vision ward so you are able to see that the gentle man ward is working.{{item:2043}}
